<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٩١٩ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/495">أَحْمَدُ بْنُ الْمِقْدَامِ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1717">خَالِدٌ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2332">سَعِيدٌ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5183">قَتَادَةَ: </a>أَنَّ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسًا </a>حَدَّثَهُمْ: <span class="c2">«أَنَّ النَّبِيَّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> رَخَّصَ لِعَبْدِ الرَّحْمَنِ بْنِ عَوْفٍ وَالزُّبَيْرِ فِي قَمِيصٍ مِنْ حَرِيرٍ مِنْ حِكَّةٍ كَانَتْ بِهِمَا.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>